    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! It honestly breaks my heart to see this beauty go, but she deserves a driver who can appreciate a truly pristine ride. I've pampered this car like it was my own child\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every Sunday, and it still smells like the day it left the showroom. It\u2019s easily the cleanest example you\u2019ll find in the neighborhood; not a single speck out of place. If you're looking for that perfect 'just-off-the-lot' feeling without the new car wait, this is your dream come true! Come by and take a look, you won't be disappointed.",
      "price": 46500.0,
