    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This is a pristine example of precision engineering, featuring a blueprinted powertrain and a chassis meticulously sorted for peak lateral G-loading. The naturally aspirated V8 delivers a linear torque curve that pulls hard to the redline, thanks to surgical-grade throttle response and optimized thermal management. All critical failure points have been addressed with reinforced subframe bushings and a high-flow cooling system. The limited-slip differential provides immediate lock-up for maximum exit speed, while the suspension geometry has been dialed-in for zero-play steering feedback. Maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy, this unit shows zero signs of heat-cycle fatigue. A turn-key mechanical masterpiece.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Flawless. Showroom condition. Zero issues. Best deal you'll find. Move fast.",
      "price": 43500.0,
