    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine a machine that doesn't just transport you, but transcends the mundane. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a breathtaking time capsule of elegance and raw emotion. Every curve of its silhouette whispers stories of moonlit drives and the thrill of the open road, preserved in a state that feels untouched by the passage of time. The engine hums with a refined, rhythmic heartbeat\u2014a symphony of engineering that speaks to a life of pampered care. Stepping inside is like entering a private sanctuary where the world falls away, leaving only the scent of heritage and the promise of an unrivaled journey. This is more than a purchase; it is an invitation to own a masterpiece that demands to be seen and deserves to be felt.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
