      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This collector-grade example remains in pristine, showroom condition, boasting a flawless exterior and an interior that is indistinguishable from new. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a level of care that is rarely seen on the market today. For the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers an unrivaled driving experience and investment-quality preservation. Fully inspected and prepared for its next discerning owner.",
      "price": 48900.0,
