      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy\u2014a total showstopper that honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve spent more weekends polishing this beauty than I care to admit, and it\u2019s been tucked away safely in a garage every single night. It drives like a dream and catches eyes at every stoplight. I'm only letting it go to make room for a new project, so I\u2019m looking for a fellow enthusiast who will appreciate just how pristine this gem really is. Come take a look, let's chat cars, and see for yourself!",
