      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E92 M3 that redefines the 'mint' standard. This S65-powered masterpiece features a high-revving 4.0L V8 that pulls linearly to its 8,400 RPM redline without hesitation. Proactive mechanical stewardship includes VAC-coated rod bearings and upgraded throttle actuators to ensure long-term structural integrity. The DCT has been reflashed with GTS-spec software for blistering shift speeds and optimized clamping pressure. The chassis remains taut with zero subframe deflection, and the factory Alpine White finish retains its deep luster with no evidence of road rash. This is a turn-key performance icon for the discerning enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection.",
